  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-01 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. This adversarial package contains an orphan Claim node whose prose description references a body of supporting simulation and experimental work but whose structured prov:wasDerivedFrom link to Evidence is absent, triggering W-EP-01.",
