    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 credibility factors. Seven factors were assessed; all achieved levels fall below required levels for MRL 5. Six factors were not assessed and flagged as epistemic gaps. The central hemolysis prediction claim is supported by an extensive prose description referencing mesh convergence, Monte Carlo UQ, and in-vitro comparison data, and is judged by the assessment team to be adequately grounded. The package is accepted for regulatory submission with the understanding that identified gaps will be addressed in a supplemental filing.",
